This Impact assessment method is an adaption of the previous PB-LCIA 2.03 for SimaPro, which was developed by Ryberg, Owsianiak, Richardson & Hauschild (2018),
Morten Ryberg has produced a CSV for implementation of PB-LCIA method in SimaPro.
To make the method available to more LCA practioners, we have created a migration of the SimaPro version to a version which conforms to the linking syntax needed for OpenLCA. The method is developed for use in OpenLCA 1.11, and is additionally tested on OpenLCA 2.0beta and OpenLCA 2.0 with good results.
Documentation: Documentation for the migration approach, including validation results and discussion is available at:
Practitioners: Lund, Manja Nørrekær & Schjerbeck, Anna Kristina & Schor, Simon Winther.
References: @article{Ryberg_Owsianiak_Richardson_Hauschild_2018, title={Development of a life-cycle impact assessment methodology linked to the planetary boundaries framework}, volume={88}, DOI={10.1016/j.ecolind.2017.12.065}, journal={Ecological Indicators}, author={Ryberg, Morten W. and Owsianiak, Mikołaj and Richardson, Katherine and Hauschild, Michael Z.}, year={2018}, pages={250–262}}
